\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Now, \'93the risk is very high\'94 that carbon output could surge past pre-pandemic levels, she says, \'93especially since we\'92ve done it in the past, not very long ago.\'94 During the 2007-08 financial crisis, emissions dropped but then bounced back.\
